OL,6,FA father deliberately set fire to his
OL,7,Fhouse with his children and their
OL,8,Ffriends inside it, a court has heard.
OL,10,FPhilip Jones, 56, committed arson at
OL,11,Fhis three-bed terraced property on
OL,12,FChepstow Road in Cwmparc, , on 6
OL,13,FSeptember last year.
OL,15,FJones made threats to burn down the
OL,16,Fhouse and told his children to leave
OL,17,Fbefore starting the blaze near the gas
OL,18,Fmetre in the living room, Merthyr
OL,19,FTydfil Crown Court heard.
