OL,4,Cwith children and friends inside
OL,6,FHis son, daughter, daughter's partner
OL,7,Fand two friends escaped the property
OL,8,Fwithout any injuries.
OL,10,FDuring sentencing, the court heard how
OL,11,Fthe defendant's action stemmed from
OL,12,Fthe effects drug use had on his mental
OL,13,Fstate, with his behaviour becoming
OL,14,F"increasingly strange" in the week
OL,15,Fleading to the incident, according to
OL,16,Fhis daughter.
