OL,3,CFather deliberately set fire to house
OL,4,Cwith children and friends inside
OL,6,FJones' son said on the day of the fire
OL,7,Fhis father was "shouting a lot of
OL,8,Fangry comments" and was "in a mood,"
OL,9,Fwhile his daughter described his as
OL,10,F"paranoid" and looking "pale."
OL,12,FHis daughter and her partner were
OL,13,Fupstairs with two friends when they
OL,14,Fheard the defendant shout: "You guys
OL,15,Fbetter get out. I'm going to set this
OL,16,Fhouse on fire right now."
OL,18,FAt first they did not know whether he
OL,19,Fwas being serious, but started to
OL,20,Fleave the house when he repeated the
OL,21,Fthreat.
