OL,4,Cwith children and friends inside
OL,6,FHis son was playing on a games console
OL,7,Fin his room when he heard the alarm go
OL,8,Foff and saw smoke outside his bedroom
OL,9,Fdoor.
OL,11,FHe initially thought his sister had
OL,12,Fleft a candle on.
OL,14,FProsecutor Jac Brown said his sister
OL,15,Ftold him to leave and said he saw "a
OL,16,Flarge fire and smoke emanating from
OL,17,Fthe front room" as he exited the house.
OL,19,FHe shouted for the family's two dogs
OL,20,Fbut Jones had removed them from the
OL,21,Fhouse shortly before starting the fire.
