OL,6,FDefending Stephen Thomas said the
OL,7,Fincident was "completely out of
OL,8,Fcharacter" for the father.
OL,10,FHe argued his guilty plea was the best
OL,11,Fmitigation, having previously admitted
OL,12,Farson being reckless as to whether
OL,13,Flife is endangered.
OL,15,FHe added the defendant's drug use had
OL,16,F"a big impact on his mental health,
OL,17,Fhis behaviours, and actions over the
OL,18,Fyear," impacting "all aspects of his
OL,19,Flife".
