OL,6,FHe added the death of Jones' partner -
OL,7,Fthe mother of his children - had
OL,8,Fcaused his mental state to deteriorate
OL,9,F"rapidly" as he increased his misuse
OL,10,Fof cannabis.
OL,12,FThe court heard how his depression
OL,13,F"deepened" due to cannabis misuse,
OL,14,Fwith his mental health improving
OL,15,Fwhilst he was in custody as he stopped
OL,16,Ftaking the drug.
OL,18,FTalking about Jones' time in custody,
OL,19,FMr Thomas said: "He has had time to
OL,20,Freflect upon what he has done and
OL,21,Funderstands the enormity of it.
