OL,6,FHe continued: "He has expressed
OL,7,Fremorse and regret of this and
OL,8,Funderstands he has lost his family as
OL,9,Fa result of his behaviour."
OL,11,FSentencing, the judge said the case
OL,12,Fgave a warning to "anyone who thinks
OL,13,Fthat cannabis is not a harmful drug,"
OL,14,Fand said the impact of using it had
OL,15,Fbeen "profound."
OL,17,FHowever, he added: "You do not suffer
OL,18,Ffrom a mental illness ` what you did
OL,19,Fstemmed from the effects of drug use
OL,20,Fupon your mental state. That is not
OL,21,Fmitigation."
