OL,6,FThe judge praised Jones for using his
OL,7,Ftime in custody "constructively" and
OL,8,Fadded he was "noted as being hard
OL,9,Fworking" when off drugs.
OL,11,FHe was sentenced to three years and
OL,12,Ffour months in prison, half of which
OL,13,Fwill be spent in custody before being
OL,14,Freleased on licence for the remainder.
